start.label: you can't teach old dog new tricks

examples.en: We have to change people's mindsets and motivate them.

examples.en: American financiers have a very different mindset from ours.

examples.en: Flexible working was part of the mindset of the company from the start.
examples.ru: Гибкий подход к работе был частью менталитета компании с самого начала.
